\c 1
\s Kwaziso
\p
\v 1 Pauro, muranda waMwari, nemuapositori waJesu Kristu, zvichienderana nerutendo rwevasanangurwa vaMwari nekuziva chokwadi chiri pakunamata Mwari,
\v 2 patariro yeupenyu husingaperi, uhwo Mwari usingagoni kureva nhema hwaakavimbisa nhambo dzenguva dzisati dzavapo,
\v 3 asi panguva dzakafanira wakaratidza shoko rake nekuparidza kwakaiswa mumaoko mangu zvichienderana nemurairo waMwari Muponesi wedu,
\v 4 kuna Tito, mwana \add wangu\add* chaiye zvichienderana nerutendo rwatinodyidzana: Nyasha, tsitsi, rugare zvinobva kuna Mwari Baba, naIshe Jesu Kristu Muponesi wedu.
\s Basa raTito paKrete
\p
\v 5 Nekuda kwaizvozvi ndakakusiya paKrete, kuti ugadzirise zvakasara, uye ugadze vatariri muguta rega-rega, sezvandakakuraira ini;
\v 6 kana aripo usina chaangapomerwa, murume wemukadzi umwe, une vana vakatendeka, vasingapiwi mhosva yekusazvidzora, kana kusateerera.
\v 7 Nokuti mutariri unofanira kuva usina chaangapomerwa, semuchengeti weimba waMwari; asina mukundo, asingakurumidzi kutsamwa, asiri muraradzi, asiri murwi, asingakariri fuma yakaipa,
\v 8 asi anofarira kugamuchira vaenzi, anoda zvakanaka, anozvidzora, wakarurama, mutsvene, anozvibata,
\v 9 anobatisisa shoko rakatendeka sezvaakadzidziswa, kuti agone kukurudzira nedzidziso mhenyu, uye kupwisa vakakavari.
\s Vadzidzisi venhema
\p
\v 10 Nokuti vazhinjiwo varipo vasingateereri, vanotaura zvisina maturo nevanyengeri, zvikuru avo vekudzingiswa,
\v 11 vanofanira kudzivira miromo yavo; vanopidigura misha yese, vachidzidzisa zvinhu zvavasingafaniri, nekuda kwefuma yakaipa.
\v 12 Umwe pakati pavo, \add unova\add* muporofita wavo pachavo, wakati: VaKrete vagara vari varevi venhema, zvikara zvakaipa, simbe dzinokara.
\v 13 Uchapupu uhu ndehwechokwadi. Nekuda kwechikonzero ichi uvatsiure zvakasimba, kuti vagwinye parutendo,
\v 14 vasingateereri ngano dzevaJudha nemirairo yevanhu vanofuratira chokwadi.
\v 15 Kune vakachena zvinhu zvese zvakachena; asi kune vakasvibiswa nevasingatendi hakuna chakachena, asi kufunga kwavowo nehana zvakasvibiswa.
\v 16 Vanobvuma kuti vanoziva Mwari, asi pamabasa vano\add mu\add*ramba, vari vanyangadzi nevasingateereri uye vasingabatsiri pabasa rese rakanaka.
